{"tid":1858312,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"先23歲但記憶超差","createTime":"2020-02-02T15:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T03:37:37.000Z","uid":273587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1937956af413ed891bd669c444152a0f6754cc94","tid":1858312,"uid":273587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"人哋係過目不忘但我係過目即忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工老細交代過我嘅野轉個頭就唔記得<br />\n同人傾計講講下會唔記得自己想講啲咩<br />\n啱啱係屋企諗住搵啲嘢 但搵搵下唔記得咗自己搵緊啲咩 俾呀妹係咁笑9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係咪腦退化 究竟有冇啲咩方法可以增強記憶力<br />\n<br />\n不過我無唔記得聽日罷工！<br />\n一齊支持醫護罷工！"},{"pid":"68af330d04b67b8c9a4563a2b922c71d50d5db1a","tid":1858312,"uid":275114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:38:17.000Z","msg":"打少D"},{"pid":"5181a385a5f254f4adf0c0b218e4d21ec071451b","tid":1858312,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"社會上下欄體力工種總要有人做"},{"pid":"f034d9509191a7c395f890531c252f93afab1550","tid":1858312,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"男定女"},{"pid":"6405a4f7d4f23c63b8b59b574f0778a87aedbffd","tid":1858312,"uid":28131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5181a385a5f254f4adf0c0b218e4d21ec071451b","tid":1858312,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"社會上下欄體力工種總要有人做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9ddc4744eb710b4a9600c6bfc0721709914b76","tid":1858312,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"寫低"},{"pid":"a7f56b3e5207ae4bf536bbb66ef409ff1500a9f6","tid":1858312,"uid":273587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f034d9509191a7c395f890531c252f93afab1550","tid":1858312,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike